END $$;
NOTICE:  Test 9 Caught expected error: On UPDATE, conflicting explicit values for valid_to and valid_until. With valid_until=05-01-2026, expected valid_to=Thu Apr 30 00:00:00 2026. Got valid_to=05-01-2026
